      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "We are pleased to present this exemplary vehicle, maintained to the highest standards of automotive excellence. This unit represents a rare opportunity to acquire a machine in pristine, showroom condition. Every detail, from the flawless exterior finish to the immaculate interior upholstery, reflects a history of meticulous care. This is a definitive choice for the discerning driver who demands uncompromising quality and peak performance.",
