      "description": "We are honored to present this superlative vehicle, maintained in an impeccable state that rivals its original delivery condition. This specimen exhibits an extraordinary level of preservation, featuring a flawless exterior finish and an interior devoid of any discernible wear. Meticulously serviced and stored in a climate-controlled environment, this vehicle represents the pinnacle of its class. For the discerning collector who demands nothing less than mechanical and aesthetic perfection, this offering stands as a definitive acquisition.",
      "price": 46500.0,
